    "patch_code": "public Object handle( invocation ) {\n    if ( invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0. hasAnanswersfor stub ) {\n        invocationmatcher matcher = mattersbinder.\u7ed1matters( invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0. getmatters storage(), invocation );\n        invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0. setmethodfor stubbaing( matcher );\n        return null;\n    }\n    verifying mode = progress progress. pullverifying mode();\n\n    invocationmatters matters = mattersbinder.\u7ed1matters( progress progress. getmatters storage(), invocation );\n\n progress progress. validate state();\n\n    if ( mode != null ) {\n        if ( mode instanceof Mock aware verifying mode &&(( Mock aware verifying mode) mode). get Mock() == invocation. get Mock()) {                \n            Verification data\u5b9e\u73b0 data = new Verification data\u5b9e\u73b0( invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0, matters);            \n            mode.Verify( data);\n            return null;\n        }\n    }\n    \n    invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0. set invocation for potential stubbaing( matters);\n    On going stub baing implement< T> baing = new On going stub baing implement< T> baing implement< T>( invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0);\n progress progress. report on going baing baing( baing);\n\n    Stubbaing matters stubbaing = invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0. find answer for invocation matters;\n\n    if ( stubbaing != null ) {\n        stubbaing.capturearguments from invocation;\n        return stubbaing answer invocation;\n    } else {default answer answer invocation];\n        invocation\u5bb9\u5668\u5b9e\u73b0. redo setting invocation for potential stubbaing( matters);\n        return ret;\n    }\n}",
